metadata.name: Legendary Shroomies #1
metadata.description:
Shhh..can you hear that...The mycelium revolution is upon us. There are so mush-room to grow when it comes to magic mushrooms. Sugar and spice and everything nice, that ºs not what magic mushrooms are made of. Instead, soils rich in quirky thoughts and peculiar imagination and everything in a temporary altered state of consciousness. 

Every Magic Shroomie is unique. Each piece of art is autogenerated from over 138+ traits & attributes. We are more than an ingredient in a pizza topping or a perfect partner for risotto. We send you on a life-changing psychedelic experience.

Dig deeper at www.magicshroomies.art.
